Teacher shot, killed in Tacoma; suspect slain

Tacoma Police officers investigate the slaying of special education teacher at Birney Elementary School in Tacoma. The suspect in the shooting was fatally shot by Pierce County sheriff's deputies shortly after. (AP Photo/The News Tribune, Dean J.
